Workflow

- Each feature must include structure, runnable code, setup steps, rationale, and at least one test.
- Keep docs current (README or /docs/feature.md).

Testing & CI

- Unit: Vitest/Jest; UI: React Testing Library; e2e: Playwright (web) / Detox (mobile).
- CI must run typecheck, lint, tests, and build.
- Pre-commit hooks: lint, typecheck, and quick tests.
